Reasoning: The paper discusses the performance analysis of a cognitive underlay system with power control mechanism, which involves channel estimation, interference power, and throughput. These topics are commonly studied in the fields of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), computer networks and communications (cs.CR), control systems (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM).
